== CopyrightSpot.com

100 Word Description:

So your a blogger, author, poet or have some original writings on the web.  Wouldn't it be nice if there was an easy and convenient way for you to monitor the web 
and discover sites that are reusing your textual content? You can feel rest assured now, CopyrightSpot is here for you. You can use this free service to help develop 
new business relationships with sites that see value in your writings. It can help with your Page Rank by allowing you to identify attribution links that are missing 
from sites that are reusing your writings. It's also a great way for you to track your already licensed material on the web.

